The XRD was used to investigate the crystal structure of TiO2 nanoparticle. These patterns of TiO2 nanoparticle have some peaks shown in Fig. 22. The peaks occur at 2θ of 25.3° for crystal plane 101and 37.90 for crystal plane (004). The result shows that the crystal structure of the TiO2 is anatase and the interlayer distance of this compound was calculated (d spacing = 3.52732 Å, and 2.34287 Å respectively); these data agree with Bagheri et al. (2013) and Ghorbanpour et al. (2015)Fig. 22
